{"tid":1952924,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣先可以暫時放低一個人？","createTime":"2020-04-01T01:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T20:38:12.000Z","uid":133557,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"fba0cecbac4561020352ae6f3ed257a20c2eb687","tid":1952924,"uid":133557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T01:40:35.000Z","msg":"之前開咗個po呻完夢到好中意嘅女仔<br />\n經過幾日反思<br />\n覺得某巴打講得好啱<br />\n<br />\n越想搵就越得唔到自己想要嘅結果<br />\n唔搵可能又自己彈出黎<br />\n<br />\n呢一生人打後都忘記佢真係覺得幾難<br />\n但呢一刻我想暫時忘記佢<br />\n比個機會自己專心專注集中<br />\n趁住呢段期間盡量想做返啲有意思嘅事叫做增值下自己<br />\n唔知幾多年後若果真有機會再見面<br />\n哪怕關係close唔到都叫有啲面去面對返人地<br />\n不至於當時嘅自己咁樣 自卑到覆人都唔敢<br />\n<br />\n但我具體應該點做...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做咩事都好 個腦都不斷彈出關於佢嘅事<br />\nFF又有 純回憶又有 現實與理想嘅交織又有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成個病態癡漢咁<br />\n自己依家完全專注唔到學習上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搵第二個對象轉移情感呢個真係唔掂<br />\n自從冇同佢聯絡後成個中學到依家完全冇對其他女仔有過咩feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7648d64e6216f0c621b65d08231a6cdc562d981","tid":1952924,"uid":317104,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T03:12:34.000Z","msg":"雖然我咁講好廢<br />\n但我記得我當年分手之後<br />\n一直做自己中意嘅興趣嚟麻醉自己<br />\n將自己嘅schedule塞滿哂<br />\n唔比自己有空閒嘅時間諗嘢<br />\n同時增值下自己個樣<br />\n開始做運動調節飲食減肥<br />\n每日都chur自己令到自己好攰<br />\n返到去飲杯熱水之後聽歌訓覺<br />\n從來唔會迫自己忘記佢 由得佢順其自然<br />\n只係想增值自己令佢知道原來我都係好好嘅人<br />\n時間耐咗 漸漸就會開始放低或者有其他發展<br />\n所以巴打可以發掘下自己嘅興趣 增值下自己<br />\n唔洗成日迫自己放低 咁樣會有反效果<br />\n越想放低 越放唔低 暫時又好 長期都好<br />\n當係為自己努力 巴打加油啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b0893f716c43250bce6694b8e5495ca95e4a63a","tid":1952924,"uid":133557,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e7648d64e6216f0c621b65d08231a6cdc562d981","tid":1952924,"uid":317104,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T03:12:34.000Z","msg":"雖然我咁講好廢<br />\n但我記得我當年分手之後<br />\n一直做自己中意嘅興趣嚟麻醉自己<br />\n將自己嘅schedule塞滿哂<br />\n唔比自己有空閒嘅時間諗嘢<br />\n同時增值下自己個樣<br />\n開始做運動調節飲食減肥<br />\n每日都chur自己令到自己好攰<br />\n返到去飲杯熱水之後聽歌訓覺<br />\n從來唔會迫自己忘記佢 由得佢順其自然<br />\n只係想增值自己令佢知道原來我都係好好嘅人<br />\n時間耐咗 漸漸就會開始放低或者有其他發展<br />\n所以巴打可以發掘下自己嘅興趣 增值下自己<br />\n唔洗成日迫自己放低 咁樣會有反效果<br />\n越想放低 越放唔低 暫時又好 長期都好<br />\n當係為自己努力 巴打加油啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T04:10:26.000Z","msg":"多謝意見<br />\n我原本都有打算做下運動減下肥 學下新嘢<br />\n可能都係因為呢排支肺<br />\n自己成日屈係屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又冇得出去行下玩下 返下part time之類<br />\n成日對住電腦手機又辛苦<br />\n情緒屈喺一個地方到影響越黎越深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望隨住時間淡化<br />\n好似你講咁順其自然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bea39f16d2a6aa044360a439da05cc5f0bdee094","tid":1952924,"uid":210995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T05:04:02.000Z","msg":"開始新一段感情"},{"pid":"aaffcdc05667d72b4e02fa1374f57f6f51209805","tid":1952924,"uid":196240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:37:52.000Z","msg":"暫時放低完 之後咪又拎翻起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4989e27efcc871bf57db66bc5ac72b44f2417f55","tid":1952924,"uid":48892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bea39f16d2a6aa044360a439da05cc5f0bdee094","tid":1952924,"uid":210995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T05:04:02.000Z","msg":"開始新一段感情"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:46:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46110cf3af747687bb9e8a013df14b7c723a765c","tid":1952924,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:48:01.000Z","msg":"返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係咁易，雖然唔知你咩事散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果係因為佢傷你而分開嘅話，你開頭會嘗試抹走呢個人形賤種嘅存在，但條疤都會照樣痛，牽連住你嘅人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f79da4708ba8cdeff3c0f45c97158895508d5ed","tid":1952924,"uid":261268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:58:20.000Z","msg":"記得幾年前分手 係用結他黎消磨時間<br />\n由零開始 每日不斷彈彈彈 彈到手指都爛曬<br />\n時間真好快過<br />\n早幾個星期又分左 頭一個星期就摺埋自己享受傷心既感覺<br />\n依加又開始拎返個結他不斷彈彈彈 時間又係好快過<br />\n搵過個係最快 但仲係好鐘意上一個 又談何容易<br />\n真係搵d野做(睇戲唔算因為你根本唔會專心到)<br />\n無辦法投入感情去第二個人度都求其搵人傾住計先<br />\n令自己分下心，一齊加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da8e6c4f2f8b1ed09790339d948e38adceb0d524","tid":1952924,"uid":164613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:03:48.000Z","msg":"痴漢心態我理解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f80955613a46879f9235fa5240f4f4038dd59941","tid":1952924,"uid":347556,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bea39f16d2a6aa044360a439da05cc5f0bdee094","tid":1952924,"uid":210995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T05:04:02.000Z","msg":"開始新一段感情"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:36:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0548d4eddeec53fd9a98c9865e19bc916f94cd42","tid":1952924,"uid":228213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f80955613a46879f9235fa5240f4f4038dd59941","tid":1952924,"uid":347556,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bea39f16d2a6aa044360a439da05cc5f0bdee094","tid":1952924,"uid":210995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T05:04:02.000Z","msg":"開始新一段感情"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:36:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T15:30:47.000Z","msg":"開始吧， 你只能選擇 向前"},{"pid":"1b5fce520dfec7bad24d5e162306ed7b07da9abe","tid":1952924,"uid":261268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f80955613a46879f9235fa5240f4f4038dd59941","tid":1952924,"uid":347556,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bea39f16d2a6aa044360a439da05cc5f0bdee094","tid":1952924,"uid":210995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T05:04:02.000Z","msg":"開始新一段感情"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:36:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T15:52:45.000Z","msg":"絲打 我同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e47b20d86fbe86a65c86c21baa74b25f653199e","tid":1952924,"uid":189103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T16:44:05.000Z","msg":"反工 不停揾野做 <br />\n最好做到自己好攰 <br />\n一撻落床就訓得着<br />\n唔洗再諗佢"},{"pid":"a58f2584d41107aacf365176b21279eeddb767fc","tid":1952924,"uid":347556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0548d4eddeec53fd9a98c9865e19bc916f94cd42","tid":1952924,"uid":228213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f80955613a46879f9235fa5240f4f4038dd59941","tid":1952924,"uid":347556,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bea39f16d2a6aa044360a439da05cc5f0bdee094","tid":1952924,"uid":210995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T05:04:02.000Z","msg":"開始新一段感情"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:36:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T15:30:47.000Z","msg":"開始吧， 你只能選擇 向前"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T17:05:45.000Z","msg":"其實係。依家只有一條路。就算有多條路，佢都只會係死路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5b3134064e90da433bb308f8ef273985a06246","tid":1952924,"uid":119401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T19:30:10.000Z","msg":"習慣諗起佢"},{"pid":"cbf4bca76cdd42f79d57a42736c932f8cd225c0c","tid":1952924,"uid":133557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T20:11:18.000Z","msg":"半夜扎醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌我依家呢個狀態好唔掂當<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c804e287e064977f3720ee6f0426420951d39a","tid":1952924,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T20:30:31.000Z","msg":"訓教"},{"pid":"4f6ceb23a9d6c4911efc04c4635ad62d0285737c","tid":1952924,"uid":127508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T20:33:08.000Z","msg":"其實你愈想避免某一樣野就會愈避免唔到，<br />\n你愈迫自己放低更加會諗起果個人，<br />\n不如你試下正向思維，<br />\n首先唔好特登去迫自己忘記，諗起佢就諗起佢，<br />\n當成一個動力，既然你呢一刻得唔到，<br />\n就努力去增值自己成為一個吸引嘅男人，<br />\n無論外型定內在都好，俾個目標自己去增值，<br />\n可能到時你得到嘅會係更多，<br />\n一直消沉唔會係出路。"},{"pid":"4c08bf4d6396116b78ba18ef5078c7e177ab3d11","tid":1952924,"uid":127508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T20:34:38.000Z","msg":"唔知你鐘唔鐘意睇文字，<br />\n但我一唔開心時會睇書，<br />\n睇啲有關心理學/小說，<br />\n個人會緩和啲。"},{"pid":"f067a91ed482b68f423619aa45ddbf42b8281e42","tid":1952924,"uid":134103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T23:05:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40754e646b790e37769d77a9ea9d48cb4de41272","tid":1952924,"uid":133557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c08bf4d6396116b78ba18ef5078c7e177ab3d11","tid":1952924,"uid":127508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T20:34:38.000Z","msg":"唔知你鐘唔鐘意睇文字，<br />\n但我一唔開心時會睇書，<br />\n睇啲有關心理學/小說，<br />\n個人會緩和啲。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T03:17:55.000Z","msg":"好似幾好<br />\n其實我幾中意睇書<br />\n小說就不了 驚睇完故仔會仲亂諗嘢<br />\n咁巴打有咩書可以推介下"},{"pid":"11f955711ca66d2ee250c1c72eddbcac4af167bf","tid":1952924,"uid":133557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f067a91ed482b68f423619aa45ddbf42b8281e42","tid":1952924,"uid":134103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco